<i>noun</i>: 적화 [저콰], 공산화 [공ː산화] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>적화 [저콰]</dt><br>
<dd>1. turning red</dd><br>
<dd>붉게 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of turning red.</dd><br>
<dd>2. communization</dd><br>
<dd>공산주의에 물듦. 또는 그렇게 되게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of being influenced, or causing to be influenced, by communism.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>공산화 [공ː산화]</dt><br>
<dd>communization</dd><br>
<dd>공산주의 사회가 되거나 되게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act or state of becoming a communist society or making a society communist.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>